Package: MetaComp
Version: 1.0.1
Title: Tools for Merging and HeatMap-like Visualization of EDGE (GOTTCHA/GOTTCHA2, bwa, Kraken, MetaPhlAn) Taxonomy Assignments
Description: Implements routines for metagenome sample taxonomy assignments collection, 
    aggregation, and visualization. Produces SVG and PDF heatmap-like plots comparing taxa abundances across projects. 
Authors@R: person("Pavel", "Senin", , "psenin@lanl.gov", c("aut", "cre"))
URL: https://github.com/seninp-bioinfo/MetaComp
BugReports: https://github.com/seninp-bioinfo/MetaComp/issues
